---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Eventos - Pecaditos">
	<!-- Events Hero -->
	<section class="events-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1 class="hero-title">Onde Vamos Pecar</h1>
			<p class="hero-subtitle">Encontra-nos nas melhores festas e eventos das Terras de Basto!</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Events Info -->
	<section class="events-info">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="info-content">
				<div class="info-text">
					<h2>A Nossa Agenda Está Sempre a Ferver!</h2>
					<p>
						Estamos sempre à procura de novos eventos e festas para levar os nossos <strong>Pecaditos</strong> até ti. 
						Desde feiras tradicionais a festivais de verão, passando por festas de juventude e eventos especiais.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Volta aqui regularmente</strong> para ficares a par das datas dos próximos eventos onde nos podes encontrar. 
						E não te esqueças de nos seguir nas redes sociais para não perderes nenhuma novidade!
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="info-visual">
					<div class="calendar-icon">📅</div>
					<div class="floating-icons">
						<span>🎪</span>
						<span>🎉</span>
						<span>🎊</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Upcoming Events -->
	<section class="upcoming-events">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Próximos Eventos</h2>
			<div class="events-grid">
				<div class="event-card coming-soon">
					<span class="event-status">Coming Soon</span>
					<div class="event-icon">🎪</div>
					<h3>Feira de São João</h3>
					<div class="event-date">Data a confirmar</div>
					<p>A tradicional feira de São João onde vamos espalhar doçura e alegria por toda a comunidade. Prepara-te para uma experiência única!</p>
				</div>

				<div class="event-card coming-soon">
					<span class="event-status">Coming Soon</span>
					<div class="event-icon">🎉</div>
					<h3>Festa da Juventude</h3>
					<div class="event-date">Data a confirmar</div>
					<p>Um evento cheio de energia jovem onde os nossos doces vão ser a sensação. Diversão garantida para todas as idades!</p>
				</div>

				<div class="event-card coming-soon">
					<span class="event-status">Coming Soon</span>
					<div class="event-icon">☀️</div>
					<h3>Festival de Verão</h3>
					<div class="event-date">Data a confirmar</div>
					<p>O calor do verão pede doces refrescantes! Vamos estar presentes com as nossas criações mais frescas e deliciosas.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="events-notice">
				<div class="notice-icon">⚠️</div>
				<p>
					<strong>Atenção:</strong> As datas dos eventos serão atualizadas em breve! 
					Segue-nos nas redes sociais para ficares a par de todas as novidades e não perderes nenhum dos nossos eventos.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Private Events -->
	<section class="private-events">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="private-content">
				<div class="private-visual">
					<div class="party-icon">🎊</div>
					<div class="celebration-icons">
						<span>🎂</span>
						<span>💒</span>
						<span>🏢</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="private-text">
					<h2>Eventos Privados</h2>
					<p>
						Tens um evento especial e queres que seja verdadeiramente <strong>doce e memorável</strong>? 
						Contrata os nossos serviços para casamentos, aniversários, festas corporativas ou qualquer celebração especial.
					</p>
					<ul class="services-list">
						<li>🎂 Aniversários e festas de família</li>
						<li>💒 Casamentos e celebrações românticas</li>
						<li>🏢 Eventos corporativos e team building</li>
						<li>🎓 Formaturas e celebrações académicas</li>
						<li>🎪 Feiras e eventos comunitários</li>
						<li>🎉 Festas temáticas e eventos especiais</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">
						<span class="btn-icon">📞</span>
						Pedir Orçamento
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Events Hero */
	.events-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream) 0%, var(--beige-light) 50%, var(--beige-dark) 100%);
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.events-hero::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="25" cy="25" r="1" fill="rgba(60,36,21,0.1)"/><circle cx="75" cy="45" r="1.5" fill="rgba(60,36,21,0.1)"/><circle cx="45" cy="85" r="1" fill="rgba(60,36,21,0.1)"/></svg>');
		animation: float 30s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
		font-size: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		color: var(--chocolate-medium);
		opacity: 0.9;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 1.6;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	/* Events Info */
	.events-info {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--warm-white);
	}

	.info-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.info-text h2 {
		font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
		font-size: 3rem;
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.info-text h2::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -10px;
		left: 0;
		width: 80px;
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--gold);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.info-text p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.info-text strong {
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.info-visual {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		position: relative;
		height: 250px;
	}

	.calendar-icon {
		font-size: 6rem;
		animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));
	}

	.floating-icons {
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.floating-icons span {
		position: absolute;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.floating-icons span:nth-child(1) {
		top: 20%;
		left: 20%;
		animation-delay: -0.5s;
	}

	.floating-icons span:nth-child(2) {
		top: 60%;
		right: 20%;
		animation-delay: -1s;
	}

	.floating-icons span:nth-child(3) {
		bottom: 20%;
		left: 50%;
		animation-delay: -1.5s;
	}

	/* Upcoming Events */
	.upcoming-events {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--beige-light), var(--beige-dark));
	}

	.section-title {
		font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
		font-size: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.section-title::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -15px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 100px;
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--gold);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.events-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.event-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream), var(--beige-light));
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(60, 36, 21, 0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.event-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		height: 4px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--chocolate-light), var(--chocolate-medium));
		transform: scaleX(0);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.event-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-10px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(60, 36, 21, 0.2);
		border-color: var(--chocolate-light);
	}

	.event-card:hover::before {
		transform: scaleX(1);
	}

	.event-card.coming-soon {
		opacity: 0.8;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #e8e8e8);
	}

	.event-card.coming-soon::before {
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #bbb, #999);
	}

	.event-icon {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.event-card h3 {
		font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
		font-size: 2rem;
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.event-card.coming-soon h3 {
		color: #666;
	}

	.event-date {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--chocolate-medium);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.event-card.coming-soon .event-date {
		color: #888;
	}

	.event-card p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.event-card.coming-soon p {
		color: #888;
	}

	.event-status {
		position: absolute;
		top: 20px;
		right: 20px;
		background: var(--chocolate-light);
		color: var(--warm-white);
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.events-notice {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff9e6, var(--beige-light));
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 15px;
		border: 2px solid var(--gold);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.notice-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.events-notice p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.events-notice strong {
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
	}

	/* Private Events */
	.private-events {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: var(--warm-white);
	}

	.private-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.private-visual {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		position: relative;
		height: 250px;
	}

	.party-icon {
		font-size: 6rem;
		animation: bounce 3s ease-in-out infinite;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));
	}

	.celebration-icons {
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.celebration-icons span {
		position: absolute;
		font-size: 2rem;
		animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.celebration-icons span:nth-child(1) {
		top: 20%;
		left: 20%;
		animation-delay: -0.5s;
	}

	.celebration-icons span:nth-child(2) {
		top: 60%;
		right: 20%;
		animation-delay: -1s;
	}

	.celebration-icons span:nth-child(3) {
		bottom: 20%;
		left: 50%;
		animation-delay: -1.5s;
	}

	.private-text h2 {
		font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
		font-size: 3rem;
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.private-text h2::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -10px;
		left: 0;
		width: 80px;
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--gold);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.private-text p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.private-text strong {
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.services-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.services-list li {
		padding: 0.8rem 0;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(60, 36, 21, 0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.services-list li:hover {
		color: var(--chocolate-dark);
		transform: translateX(10px);
	}

	.services-list li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	/* Button Styles */
	.btn {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--chocolate-medium), var(--chocolate-dark));
		color: var(--warm-white);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(60, 36, 21, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(60, 36, 21, 0.4);
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--chocolate-dark), var(--chocolate-medium));
	}

	.btn-icon {
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	/* Animations */
	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(5deg); }
	}

	@keyframes bounce {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.05); }
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
		50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
	}

	/* Mobile-First Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.events-hero {
			padding: 3rem 0;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.events-info, .upcoming-events, .private-events {
			padding: 3rem 0;
		}

		.info-content, .private-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}

		.info-text h2, .private-text h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.info-text h2::after, .private-text h2::after {
			left: 50%;
			transform: translateX(-50%);
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.events-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}

		.event-card {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.event-card h3 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}

		.events-notice {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
			gap: 1rem;
		}

		.info-visual, .private-visual {
			height: 200px;
		}

		.calendar-icon, .party-icon {
			font-size: 5rem;
		}

		.floating-icons span, .celebration-icons span {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.btn {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 250px;
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.container {
			padding: 0 15px;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.info-text h2, .private-text h2 {
			font-size: 2.2rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2.2rem;
		}

		.event-card {
			padding: 1.8rem 1.2rem;
		}

		.event-icon {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}

		.event-card h3 {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
		}

		.events-notice {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.info-text p, .private-text p {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.calendar-icon, .party-icon {
			font-size: 4.5rem;
		}

		.floating-icons span, .celebration-icons span {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}

		.btn {
			padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
	}
</style>